<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavaruṣaṁbu 1351 Agu nēṁṭi<unclear>śiddhā rdhi</unclear> 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>saṁvatsara<unclear>ca</unclear>yitra śu 15 <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> yatyavāramaṁdu 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>la sōmagrahaṇa puṇyakālamaṁ 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>du śrīmahādēvicerḍla ceṁnakēśavape 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rumāḷa nagari muṁdaṭi maṁḍḍa 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pamaṁdula raṁgamadhyamu bhinna 
<lb n="7"/>mayi vuṁḍḍaṁgānu krottagānu 
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> sunapaṭṭalu nālugunnu raṁga 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>madhyapu ṟāyiṁni Ācavukamu 
<lb n="10"/>tirigi vaccina cappeṭanu dēvarana 
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> gārānu cenukāli vīrapanāyiniṁgā 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ri komāruṁḍu gōpānāyiniṁgāru tama taṁḍri vīra 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>panāyiniṁgārikiṁnni tama Aṁnna baddā 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nāyiniṁgārikiṁnni tama tōḍaṁbu 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṭna AṁnnaAṁnamanāyiniṁgāriki 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>nniṁ buṇyamugāṁ jēyiṁccina varu 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṁbani maṁgaḷamahāśrīśrīśrī <unclear>rā</unclear> 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>vūrimācōju hastaṁ varuṁbani 
</p>

